text: James Edward Doyle, Jr., (born November 23, 1945) is an American lawyer and politician. He is a member of the Democratic Party. He was the 44th Governor of Wisconsin from January 6, 2003 to January 3, 2011. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Educators from Wisconsin Category:Living people Category:Lawyers from Washington, D.C.
